		A typical gmail setup:
		incoming: 	IMAP: imap.gmail.com:993 (recommended)
				POP3: pop3.gmail.com:995
				Required SSL
		outgoing: 	smtp.gmail.com:587
				Required TLS
		
		A typical hotmail setup:
		incoming: 	pop3.live.com:995
				Required SSL
		outgoing: 	smtp.live.com:587
				Required TLS
		
		aspell-en & gnome-icon-theme are recommended."
